<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-10-11T14:44:03-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-10-11T14:44:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T14:44:03-04:00</updated><title>您一定要观看这个关于定制麦当劳壁画的精彩演示</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Panic 的 Cabel Sasser 在 XOXO 2024 舞台上的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7uPtxGxNycopAiG_09u7TwG8CqA=/300x0:1920x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647690/videoframe_298102.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;XOXO 2024 上 Panic 的 Cabel Sasser。&lt;/em>; |图片：XOXO Fest&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NY2TmY&quot;>;我知道互联网上有很多事情可做，但你真的应该停止你正在做的事情并观看&lt;a href=&quot;https: //youtu.be/Df_K7pIsfvg?feature=shared&quot;>;这个 19 分钟的演讲&lt;/a>;，内容涉及曾经位于麦当劳内的定制壁画。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;nBL9qr&quot;>;演讲由2024 年 XOXO Fest 上的《Panic》中的 Cabel Sasser 充满了愚蠢和深入意想不到的兔子洞。 （我对 Panic 的创始人抱有同样的期望，这家公司背后有一些异想天开的东西，比如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23025390/playdate-handheld-portable-gaming-console-review&quot;>; Playdate 手持设备&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/9/20/20868532/untitled-goose-game-review-nintendo-switch-pc-house-panic&quot;>;&lt; em>;无题鹅游戏&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;。&lt;/em>;）大部分演示都是关于壁画背后鲜为人知的艺术家，&lt;a href=&quot;https://wescook.art/ &quot;>;已故的韦斯库克&lt;/a>;，他还制作了一些存在于真实主题公园中的令人难以置信的设计。了解库克如此之多真是令人着迷，震荡波演讲的结尾也太棒了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5WyUzr&quot;>;演讲的每一分钟都是......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24230990/mcdonalds-bespoke-painting-cabel-sasser-wes-cook-xoxo-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24230990/mcdonalds-bespoke-painting-cabel-sasser-wes-cook-xoxo-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24230990/mcdonalds-bespoke-painting-cabel-sasser-wes-cook-xoxo-2024</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T14:02:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T14:02:30-04:00</updated><title>在 11 月发布之前，您仍然可以在这里预购 PS5 Pro</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;PlayStation 5 Pro 和控制器。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QSFMytm84sXqPDb6bA5jDj4xIkk=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612266/ps5_pro_sean_hollister_verge_003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;标准版 PS5 Pro 可能看起来不如周年纪念版那么酷，但上手要容易得多。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Sean Hollister / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Q2b2U8&quot;>;我们距离 PlayStation 5 的中期更新越来越近了，因为索尼即将推出的游戏机现已可以预订群众。虽然售价 699.99 美元的机器最初是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us% 专属的2Fbuy-consoles%2Fplaystation5-pro-console&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24252575%2Fsony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release- date&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;PlayStation Direct 店面&lt;/a>;，现已在所有主要零售商处接受预订 - 包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp /B0DGY63Z2H?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383 ?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FPLAYSTATION-PS5-PRO-CONSOLE%2F11839818124&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a >;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cnhjOAAwpA4&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u =https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fplaystation-5-pro-console%2F-%2FA-93620188&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;目标&lt;/a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;AG1DSF&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component -data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;我玩过 PS5 Pro，它显然更好&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/25/24253649 /ps5-pro-preview&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;PlayStation 5 和 PS5 Pro 之间的真正区别是什么？&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/ 11/24241002/playstation-5-ps5-pro-comparison-differences-specs-software-ray-tracing&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;PlayStation 30 周年纪念版 PS5 和 PS5 Pro 非常复古&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24249013/sony-playstation-ps5-pro-30th-anniversary-retro&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;rRD9pe&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24249013/sony-playstation-ps5-pro-30th-anniversary-retro&quot;>;索尼复古风格 30 周年纪念&lt;/a>; 主机和配件也与标准版 PS5 Pro 同时开放预购，但不幸的是，它们很快就售空了，而且仍然缺货。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;05E7SC&quot;>;无论您使用哪种 PS5 Pro 型号，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24167932/ps5 的主要前景-pro-sony-specs-announcement&quot;>;PS5 Pro&lt;/a>; 改进了图形和性能。新主机可能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240906/sony-ps5-pro-disc-drive-separate-price&quot;>;缺少光盘驱动器&lt;/a>; （您可以通过&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CL5HJNLM?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;额外 80 美元购买一个&lt;/a >;），但它是新的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release -日期&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T13:38:57-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T13:38:57-04:00</updated><title> Imgur 对成人幽默的模因将不再那么严格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Imgur 的主页。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gsH5NzugPfcr4cuQUREQG6vBEik=/0x0:750x500/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647568/3_Homepage.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Imgur&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;T0ES21&quot;>;该公司宣布，图像托管服务 Imgur 上的模因“包含成人幽默的引用”将不再被视为成熟&lt;a href =&quot;https://imgur.com/gallery/greetings-imgurians-q4-2024-update-KBefaiM&quot;>;在一篇文章中&lt;/a>;解决了内容审核政策的变化。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;74mITz&quot;>;Imgur 一直是模因历史的重要组成部分，其创建者提供了这项服务&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/reddit.com/comments /7zlyd/my_gift_to_reddit_i_created_an_image_hosting/&quot;>;2009 年作为“送给 Reddit 的礼物”。&lt;/a>; 当时，大多数平台都没有托管自己的图片，因此您必须将它们上传到第三方平台。我记得当时在 Something Awful 论坛上也经常看到 Imgur，尽管去年其他政策变化导致了 Imgur 的删除 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/20 /23691156/imgur-porn-ban- Sexly-explicit-content-terms-of-service&quot;>;非活动内容和色情内容&lt;/a>;，用户&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/ 5/8/23713128/something-awful-imgur-download-caper-digital-preservation-photo-hosting&quot;>;紧急保存旧图像&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;CvLtfy&quot;>;已宣布的更改本周可能意味着您会在...上看到更辛辣的表情包&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267304/imgur-less-strict- memes-adult-humor-content-moderation-mature&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267304/imgur-less-strict-memes-adult-humor-content-moderation-mature" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267304/imgur-less-strict-memes-adult-humor-content-moderation-mature</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T13:36:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T13:36:34-04:00</updated><title> Adam Mosseri 承认 Threads 的节制不善存在“错误”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Threads 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/s0MhXR0alG1OncdtgGawXkv61gM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73647560/STK156_Instagram_threads_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;gmjroU&quot;>;Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri 承认最近在 Meta 审核中犯下的错误Threads 和 Instagram 上的流程。例如，Meta 本周意外删除了我的帐户，因为它认为我未成年，该公司锁定了我同事的帐户，因为她开玩笑说要在热浪中死去，而其他人则看到他们的帖子消失了theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited&quot;>;没有明确的原因&lt;/a>;。 “线程审核失败”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/search?q=Threads%20Moderation%20Failures&quot;>;本周成为趋势&lt;/a>; — 给 Meta 的审核流程带来了更大的压力。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;0LEYEB&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Instagram 和 Threads 审核失控&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation- account-post-deleted-limited&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;AaB8bf&quot;>;现在 Mosseri 承认 Meta 在这些流程中存在问题，并公开发布了这一承认在线程上。他解释说，有一个“工具”坏了，它显然没有在人类评论者发帖之前向他们显示“足够的背景”，并且......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/10/11/24267898/mosseri-acknowledges-mistakes-threads-instagram-broken-moderation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267898/mosseri-acknowledges-mistakes-threads-instagram-broken-moderation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267898/mosseri-acknowledges-mistakes-threads-instagram-broken-moderation</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T13:14:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T13:14:15-04:00</updated><title> Thrustmaster（图马思特）为赛车模拟游戏控制台带来直接驱动方向盘</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Thrustmaster 的 T598 赛车方向盘位于 Raceline Pedals LTE 旁边。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VNtxGa25uiZIBaWVfuCmgV9_ABs=/0x0:934x623/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647510/thrustmaster2.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Thrustmaster T598 采用由轴向磁通电动机驱动的直接轴向驱动器。&lt;/em>; |图片：Thrustmaster&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;qNkfsm&quot;>;Thrustmaster 宣布推出新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thrustmaster.com/en-us/products/t598/&quot;>;转向系统轴距&lt;/a>;使该公司的直接驱动技术首次应用于游戏机。它还引入了一种新的电动机设计 - 已经在高端混合动力跑车上使用，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ferrari.com/en-EN/auto/sf90-stradale&quot;>;法拉利 SF90&lt; /a>; — 进入模拟赛车世界，在缩小硬件体积的同时提高真实感。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;FVnMKN&quot;>;Thrustmaster T598 即日起即可预订，价格为 499.99 美元（包括一套赛车踏板），并将将于 10 月 19 日开始发售。虽然它与 PC 和游戏机兼容，但仅限于 PlayStation 4 和 5。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XrXigu&quot;>;直接驱动模拟赛车方向盘底座通常受到爱好者的青睐，因为方向盘直接连接到电动机，而不是...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267818/thrustmaster-racing-sim-wheel- t598-sony-playstation-direct-axis-drive&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267818/thrustmaster-racing-sim-wheel-t598-sony-playstation-direct-axial-drive" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267818/thrustmaster-racing-sim-wheel-t598-sony-playstation-direct-axis-drive</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T13:11:39-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T13:11:39-04:00</updated><title>马克斯·布朗利 (Marques Brownlee) 表示，面板“我们在价格上失败了”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自 MKBHD 面板视频的图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XDjDxcQ_y3GR6QpSGvPkwW8w3mw=/74x0:1994x1280/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647509/videoframe_19176__1_.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：MKBHD&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;KrxegB&quot;>;Marques Brownlee 发布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=65ciAONXv0M&quot;>;关于的视频周五&lt;/a>;回应了围绕他的新壁纸应用程序 &lt;a href=&quot;https://panels.art/&quot;>;Panels&lt;/a>; 的批评，称他和团队在发布时“在价格方面失败了” 。该应用收到了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/24/24253023/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-response-criticism&quot;>;来自粉丝的大量批评&lt;/a>;，无论是在 MKBHD YouTube 频道还是跨社交平台。在讨论该应用程序时，布朗利承认它需要改进。 “如果我正在审查这个应用程序，我就不会很好，”他说。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;qoQ1uy&quot;>;对该应用程序的主要批评之一是高级“Panels Plus”订阅费用每月 11.99 美元或每年 49.99 美元即可删除广告并完全访问可用的壁纸集。为了让事情变得更好，Brownlee 和团队一直在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/4/24262350/mkbhd-panels-wallpaper-app-fewer-ads-update&quot;>;改进免费体验&lt;/a>;通过摆脱信息流广告，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267900/marques -brownlee-mkbhd-price-panels-wallpaper-app&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267900/marques-brownlee-mkbhd-price-panels-wallpaper-app" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267900/marques-brownlee-mkbhd-price-panels-wallpaper-app</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T12:45:19-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T12:45:19-04:00</updated><title> X 撤销联合利华的“广告商抵制”诉讼</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;X 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MhmZ1zN8ekySHTCPgryTal_Kj1A=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647426/STK160_X_TWITTER_2__B.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;GDsI42&quot;>;X 正在放弃对联合利华的索赔 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/6 /24214536/x-elon-musk-antitrust-lawsuit-advertisers-boycott&quot;>;其诉讼&lt;/a>;，指控广告商和品牌参与该公司的“非法抵制”。针对联合利华的索赔，该公司拥有多芬和赫尔曼等家喻户晓的品牌，&lt;a href=&quot;https://storage.courtlistener.com/recap/gov.uscourts.txnd.393003/gov.uscourts.txnd.393003.60.0.pdf &quot;>;今天被解雇&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;G9v4gI&quot;>;去年秋天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/20/23970274/x- elon-musk-media-matters-lawsuit-nazi-ads-filed&quot;>;X 还起诉了非营利组织 Media Matters for America&lt;/a>;，试图在事件发生后让该组织保持沉默&lt;a href=&quot;https://www. mediamatters.org/twitter/musk-endorses-antisemitic-conspiracy-theory-x-has-been-placing-ads-apple-bravo-ibm-oracle&quot;>;报道&lt;/a>;苹果和 IBM 等主要品牌的广告与纳粹内容一起出现。报告发布后，IBM &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ft.com/content/647b4c4d-f4d5-46cd-bc26-8c943b6995e7&quot;>;暂停了 X 上的广告&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;qMXKnR&quot;>;这只是马斯克针对批评者和前商业伙伴提起的诉讼之一，因为他还第二次起诉 OpenAI 及其创始人 Sam Altman 和 Greg Brockman。 （马斯克&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/1/24087937/elon-musk-suing-openai-nightmare-1l-contracts-exam&quot;>;之前提交&lt;/a>;和&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/11/24176462/elon-musk-openai-lawsuit-sam-altman-dropped&quot;>;然后早些时候放弃了&lt;/a>;类似的诉讼...... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267784/x-unilever-lawsuit-advertiser-boycott-garm-elon-musk&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267784/x-unilever-lawsuit-advertiser-boycott-garm-elon-musk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267784/x-unilever-lawsuit-advertiser-boycott-garm-elon-musk</id><author><name>佐藤米亚</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T12:26:44-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T12:26:44-04:00</updated><title>苹果的 USB SuperDrive 可能会永远消失</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple USB SuperDrive 的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Ywn7BhkK9uqqNYoC38-lwOC3CI8=/0x148:2000x1481/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647385/MD564.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mj4Rxy&quot;>;Apple 的 USB SuperDrive 在 Apple 在线商店中显示为“在所有国家/地区已售完或不可用”，&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.macrumors.com/2024/10/11/apple-quietly-discontinues-16-year-old-accessory/&quot;>;&lt;em>;MacRumors&lt;/em>; 报告&lt;/a>;，这可能表明Apple 已停产 CD/DVD 播放器。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8QZCFw&quot;>;苹果可能不再使用 SuperDrive，这并不令人意外。该产品于 2008 年首次与第一代 MacBook Air 一起推出，当时它没有光驱，所以它已经相当老了。今年早些时候，SuperDrive 在苹果美国在线商店上显示为“售罄”。尽管最近有多次提醒 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/5/23989290/playstation-digital -ownership-sucks&quot;>;为什么数字所有权很糟糕&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SfMEgb&quot;>;苹果没有立即回复置评请求。该公司的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MD564LL/A/apple-usb-superdrive&quot;>;SuperDrive 列表&lt;/a>;仍在...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267842/apple-usb-superdrive-discontinued&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267842/apple-usb-superdrive-discontinued" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267842/apple-usb-superdrive-discontinued</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T11:08:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T11:08:55-04:00</updated><title>特斯拉 Cyber​​cab 是一款外观很酷的原型车，但它需要做的远不止于此</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Tesla Cyber​​cab&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3R4O8eJdbcdTnLplnYGKC11DYj4=/0x0:7680x5120/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73647231/Robotaxi_89.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：特斯拉&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;埃隆·马斯克许诺了一个更光明的未来，但相信他需要巨大的信念飞跃。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267727/tesla-cybercab-unanswered-questions-fsd-safety-liability&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267727/tesla-cybercab-unanswered-questions-fsd-safety-liability" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267727/tesla-cybercab-unanswered-questions-fsd-safety-liability</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-11T11:03:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-11T11:03:33-04:00</updated><title> Beats Pill 扬声器比 Prime Day 期间更便宜</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2024 Beats Pill 便携式蓝牙扬声器的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/q_dizWR0EXOgP4RSOCzEo4PlXvM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73647214/DSCF7829.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;当然它看起来像药丸。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sMqn81&quot;>;我们已经远远超过了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime- day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;Prime Day Redux&lt;/a>; 现已推出，但促销中的几项出色优惠仍在进行中。事实上，有些商品甚至比两天促销期间的商品还要好——即使只是一点点。红色的 &lt;strong>;Beats Pill&lt;/strong>; 便携式蓝牙扬声器现价 97.99 美元（立减 52 美元），网址为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Beats-Pill-Compatible-Built-Microphone/dp例如，/B0D4STD5ZC?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，比我们上周创下的历史最低价便宜 1 美元。它仍然可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Beats-Pill-Compatible-Built-Microphone/dp/B0D4STT6C2?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken 购买，价格为 99.99 美元（折扣 50 美元） nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;金色&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Beats-Pill-Compatible-Built-Microphone/dp/B0D4SX9RC6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;黑色&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;EmhWbY&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Beats 期待已久的 Powerbeats Pro 2 耳机将于 2025 年上市 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24235247/beats-powerbeats-pro-2-announced-teaser-design&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bose 的全新 SoundLink Home 是最好的之一-寻找无线扬声器 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259408/bose-bluetooth-wireless-speaker-soundlink-home&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Soundcore 的新产品24.99 美元的防水扬声器几乎是冲动购买&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248304/soundcore-anker-bluetooth-speaker-portable&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;t6TaVS&quot;>;药丸形扬声器代表着该品牌在该类别中的强势回归。这是继 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/1/10/22876792/apple-beats-pill-plus-battery- power-speaker-discontinued&quot;>;Pill Plus 已于 2022 年停产&lt;/a>;。 Apple 改进了原版的迷人设计，并以受欢迎的现代性改进了其整个功能集...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267717/beats- pil-speaker-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max-bundle-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267717/beats-pill-speaker-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max-bundle-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/11/24267717/beats-pill-speaker-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max-bundle-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry></feed>